# ChatBot App (Laravel 12 + OAuth2 + Passport)

This is a Laravel 12-based ChatBot application built for a recruitment test. It includes OAuth2 authentication using Laravel Passport, multi-factor authentication (MFA), CRUD operations, a follow-up module, and real-time chat features.

